Module eu.lilithmonodia.winestock
Package eu.lilithmonodia.winestock.exceptions

Enum Class Errors

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<Errors>
eu.lilithmonodia.winestock.exceptions.Errors
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Errors>, Constable
public enum Errors extends Enum<Errors>
The Errors enum represents a list of error messages that can be used throughout the application. Each enum value represents a specific error message.
